\\\\n   58: | `ApplyLegacyDryRun()` | 메서드 | legacy dry-run 경로 |\\\\r\\\\n   59: | `RunLegacyPostApply()` | 메서드 | legacy post-apply 검사 |\\\\r\\\\n   60: | `IsAlreadyAppliedWithLog()` | 메서드 | v1 log 기반 멱등 판정(contract binding 불가) |\\\\r\\\\n   61: | `ValidateHumanDecision()` | 메서드 | ★ AI가 임의 JSON을 써서 자기 승인 위조 가능했던 구멍 |\\\\r\\\\n   62: | `ValidateRequest()` | 메서드 | legacy request 검증 |\\\\r\\\\n   63: | `ValidateCandidate()` | 메서드 | legacy candidate 검증 |\\\\r\\\\n   64: | `LegacyPostApplyError()` | 메서드 | legacy 오류 출력 |\\\\r\\\\n   65: | `ParseLegacyArgs()` | 메서드 | legacy 인자 파싱 |\\\\r\\\\n   66: | `Root` 필드 (PrepareOptions, ApplyOptions) | 레코드 필드 | `--root` 플래그 지원용, `canonicalMode` 분기의 원인 |\\\\r\\\\n   67: \\\\r\\\\n   68: ### 추가된/수정된 코드 (StateApplierCli.cs)\\\\r\\\\n   69: \\\\r\\\\n   70: | 항목 | 변경 내용 |\\\\r\\\\n   71: | --- | --- |\\\\r\\\\n   72: | `ValidTransitionKinds` | 허용 종류 명시적 집합: NORMAL, PHASE_CHANGE, RECOVERY, REPLAY |\\\\r\\\\n   73: | `FailAfterWriteHook` | `internal static Func<string?>?` — in-process seam. 환경변수·CLI에서 켤 수 없음 |\\\\r\\\\n   74: | `CheckExistingTransition()` | contract hash를 envelope 필드로부터 재계산 → log hash 비교(collision), 그 뒤 self-reported 비교(mismatch) |\\\\r\\\\n   75: | `LoadWorkstateContext()` | RunApply() 81줄 위반 해소용 헬퍼 |\\\\r\\\\n   76: | `Run()` | prepare/apply 외 인자 조합 → exit 2 usage |\\\\r\\\\n   77: | `RunApply()` | unknown kind fail-closed 먼저, canonicalMode 제거, projection 항상 실행 |\\\\r\\\\n   78: | `RunApplyCommitPhase()` | 환경변수 읽기 제거, FailAfterWriteHook in-process 훅으로 교체 |\\\\r\\\\n   79: | `Rollback()` | canonicalMode 제거, projection 항상 실행 |\\\\r\\\\n   80: \\\\r\\\\n   81: ## 반증 시험 (negative test) ※필수\\\\r\\\\n   82: \\\\r\\\\n   83: ### ★ 완료 기준 5·6·10·13 — 뚫렸다 → 막았다\\\\r\\\\n   84: \\\\r\\\\n   85: **테스트 #5: transition-id-collision**\\\\r\\\\n   86: \\\\r\\\\n   87: 뚫렸다(06C-1 구식 코드 동작):\\\\r\\\\n   88: - `envelope.transitionContractSha256`을 log의 hash와 직접 비교. 공격: 성공 로그에서 contractHash를 복사해 다른 effectiveAt을 가진 동일 transitionId 재요청에 심으면, 서로 다른 내용의 요청이 `idempotent exit 0`으로 통과됨.\\\\r\\\\n   89: \\\\r\\\\n   90: 막았다(현재 코드):\\\\r\\\\n   91: ```\\\\r\\\\n   92: envelope(T-TEST-001, effectiveAt=\\\\\\\"2099-01-01T00:00:00Z\\\\\\\", contractSha=<original>) 적용 시도\\\\r\\\\n   93: → Exit: 1\\\\r\\\\n   94: STDERR: {\\\\\\\"ok\\\\\\\":false,\\\\\\\"transitionId\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"T-TEST-001\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"reason\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"transition-id-collision\\\\\\\",\\\\r\\\\n   95:   \\\\\\\"detail\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"id 'T-TEST-001'는 다른 contract hash로 이미 적용됨\\\\\\\"}\\\\r\\\\n   96: ```\\\\r\\\\n   97: 필드에서 재계산: sha256(effectiveAt=2099...|postHash|preHash|reqHash|T-TEST-001|NORMAL) ≠ log에 저장된 hash → collision\\\\r\\\\n   98: \\\\r\\\\n   99: ---\\\\r\\\\n  100: \\\\r\\\\n  101: **테스트 #6: envelope-contract-mismatch**\\\\r\\\\n  102: \\\\r\\\\n  103: 뚫렸다(06C-1 구식 코드 동작):\\\\r\\\\n  104: - 동일 fields, self-reported hash를 `\\\\\\\"aaaa...\\\\\\\"` 로 위조. 구식 코드는 self-reported를 log와 비교만 했으므로 envelope 내부 self-consistency 검사가 없었음. 새 전이(state 미포함)에서 위조된 hash가 통과할 수 있는 경로 존재.\\\\r\\\\n  105: \\\\r\\\\n  106: 막았다(현재 코드):\\\\r\\\\n  107: ```\\\\r\\\\n  108: envelope(T-TEST-001, 원본 fields, transitionContractSha256=\\\\\\\"aaaa...\\\\\\\") 적용 시도\\\\r\\\\n  109: → Exit: 1\\\\r\\\\n  110: STDERR: {\\\\\\\"ok\\\\\\\":false,\\\\\\\"transitionId\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"T-TEST-001\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"reason\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"envelope-contract-mismatch\\\\\\\",\\\\r\\\\n  111:   \\\\\\\"detail\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"envelope.transitionContractSha256이 계산값과 다릅니다 — 위조 또는 수정됨\\\\\\\"}\\\\r\\\\n  112: ```\\\\r\\\\n  113: computed hash from fields == log hash (collision 없음) → 이후 self-reported `\\\\\\\"aaaa...\\\\\\\"` ≠ computed → mismatch\\\\r\\\\n  114: \\\\r\\\\n  115: ---\\\\r\\\\n  116: \\\\r\\\\n  117: **테스트 #10: 환경변수 무효 확인**\\\\r\\\\n  118: \\\\r\\\\n  119: 뚫렸다(06C-1 구식 코드 동작):\\\\r\\\\n  120: - `_ST_SEAM_FAIL_AFTER_WRITE=1` 환경변수를 읽어 atomic write 직후 강제 rollback을 일으켰음. 환경변수는 자식 프로세스로 상속되므로 production 진입점(환경변수)에서 실패를 주입할 수 있었음.\\\\r\\\\n  121: \\\\r\\\\n  122: 막았다(현재 코드):\\\\r\\\\n  123: ```\\\\r\\\\n  124: _ST_SEAM_FAIL_AFTER_WRITE=1 설정 후 정상 apply 실행\\\\r\\\\n  125: → Exit: 0\\\\r\\\\n  126: STDOUT: {\\\\\\\"ok\\\\\\\":true,\\\\\\\"transitionId\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"T-D01\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"previousStatus\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"in_progress\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"newStatus\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"verifying\\\\\\\",...}\\\\r\\\\n  127: ```\\\\r\\\\n  128: 코드가 환경변수를 읽지 않음. `FailAfterWriteHook`은 `internal static`이며 외부(CLI·환경변수·설정파일)에서 접근 불가.\\\\r\\\\n  129: \\\\r\\\\n  130: ---\\\\r\\\\n  131: \\\\r\\\\n  132: **테스트 #13: callsite-check 범위 확인**\\\\r\\\\n  133: \\\\r\\\\n  134: 뚫렸다(06C-1 구식 코드 동작):\\\\r\\\\n  135: - `outputs/launch/`를 historical allowlist에 포함시켜 활성 발사 프롬프트를 스캔하지 않았음 → legacy 호출이 있어도 `legacyCallsiteCount=0`으로 거짓 통과.\\\\r\\\\n  136: \\\\r\\\\n  137: 막았다(현재 코드):\\\\r\\\\n  138: ```\\\\r\\\\n  139: outputs/launch/test-legacy-call.ps1 생성 (내용: \\\\\\\"state-transition --transition-id TEST\\\\\\\") 후:\\\\r\\\\n  140: → Exit: 1, legacyCallsiteCount=1\\\\r\\\\n  141: 파일 삭제 후:\\\\r\\\\n  142: → Exit: 0, legacyCallsiteCount=0, scannedActiveFiles=329\\\\r\\\\n  143: ```\\\\r\\\\n  144: \\\\r\\\\n  145: ---\\\\r\\\\n  146: \\\\r\\\\n  147: ### 전체 판정선\\\\r\\\\n  148: \\\\r\\\\n  149: | # | 시험 | 기대 exit | 실제 exit | 판정 |\\\\r\\\\n  150: | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\\\\r\\\\n  151: | 1 | build -c Release | 0 | 0 | PASS |\\\\r\\\\n  152: | 2 | legacy 인자 (--transition-id) | 2 | 2 | PASS |\\\\r\\\\n  153: | 2 | legacy 인자 (--human-decision) | 2 | 2 | PASS |\\\\r\\\\n  154: | 3 | NORMAL prepare→apply 왕복 (픽스처, cwd=픽스처) | 0 | 0 | PASS |\\\\r\\\\n  155: | 4 | 같은 envelope 재적용 (idempotent) | 0 | 0 | PASS |\\\\r\\\\n  156: | 5 ★ | 다른 effectiveAt으로 같은 transitionId 재요청 | 1 | 1 | PASS (transition-id-collision) |\\\\r\\\\n  157: | 6 ★ | envelope.transitionContractSha256 위조 | 1 | 1 | PASS (envelope-contract-mismatch) |\\\\r\\\\n  158: | 7 | state에 가짜 id, log 없음 → reconciliation 차단 | 1 | 1 | PASS (state-corrupted-preapply) |\\\\r\\\\n  159: | 8 | candidate 1바이트 변조 | 1 | 1 | PASS (candidate-tampered) |\\\\r\\\\n  160: | 9 | in-process 훅으로 atomic write 직후 실패 주입 | 1 | — | NOT_VERIFIED |\\\\r\\\\n  161: | 10 ★ | 환경변수 _ST_SEAM_FAIL_AFTER_WRITE=1 설정 후 정상 apply | 0 | 0 | PASS (환경변수 무효) |\\\\r\\\\n  162: | 11 | transitionKind=\\\\\\\"EVIL\\\\\\\" | 1 | 1 | PASS (unknown-transition-kind) |\\\\r\\\\n  163: | 12 | transitionKind=\\\\\\\"PHASE_CHANGE\\\\\\\" | 1 | 1 | PASS (trusted-human-receipt-required) |\\\\r\\\\n  164: | 13 ★ | outputs/launch/ 에 legacy 호출 심고 callsite-check | 1 | 1 | PASS (legacyCallsiteCount=1) |\\\\r\\\\n  165: | 14 | 심은 파일 제거 후 callsite-check | 0 | 0 | PASS |\\\\r\\\\n  166: | 15 | at-rest handoff-integrity | 1 | 1 | PASS (failures=1 설계된 참양성) |\\\\r\\\\n  167: | 16 | measure dev-pack (-c Release) | 0 | 0 | PASS |\\\\r\\\\n  168: \\\\r\\\\n  169: #### 테스트 #9 NOT_VERIFIED 사유\\\\r\\\\n  170: \\\\r\\\\n  171: `FailAfterWriteHook`은 `internal static Func<string?>?`이며, 같은 프로세스의 자기 시험 코드만 설정할 수 있다. `dotnet exec`는 매번 새 프로세스를 생성하므로 외부에서 훅을 설정할 수 없다. `state-transition self-test` 부속 명령을 추가하면 검증 가능하지만, 이번 지시서에 해당 명령이 없으므로 NOT_VERIFIED로 남긴다.\\\\r\\\\n  172: \\\\r\\\\n  173: ## 검수 기준 자가점검표\\\\r\\\\n  174: | # | 기준 | 결과 | 근거 |\\\\r\\\\n  175: | --- | --- | --- | --- |\\\\r\\\\n  176: | 1 | legacy 단일-샷 경로 완전 삭제 | PASS | Run(), 인자 파싱 모두 삭제됨 — 테스트 #2 실증 |\\\\r\\\\n  177: | 2 | contract hash 재계산 (envelope 자기신고 불신) | PASS | ComputeContractHash() 필드 재계산 — 테스트 #5, #6 실증 |\\\\r\\\\n  178: | 3 | test seam 환경변수 제거 | PASS | FailAfterWriteHook in-process 전용 — 테스트 #10 실증 |\\\\r\\\\n  179: | 4 | --root / canonicalMode 제거 | PASS | PrepareOptions·ApplyOptions에 Root 없음, projection 항상 실행 |\\\\r\\\\n  180: | 5 | unknown transitionKind fail-closed | PASS | ValidTransitionKinds 집합 — 테스트 #11 실증 |\\\\r\\\\n  181: | 6 | callsite-check 범위 수정 | PASS | outputs/launch/ 활성화, .md 추가 — 테스트 #13, #14 실증 |\\\\r\\\\n  182: | 7 | RECOVERY.md 무접촉 | PASS | 파일 수정 없음 (파손 사실만 보고) |\\\\r\\\\n  183: \\\\r\\\\n  184: ## RECOVERY.md 파손 보고 (06H가 수정해야 한다)\\\\r\\\\n  185: \\\\r\\\\n  186: **