,\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"permissionMode\":\"bypassPermissions\",\"slash_commands\":[\"update-config\",\"debug\",\"simplify\",\"batch\",\"fewer-permission-prompts\",\"loop\",\"schedule\",\"claude-api\",\"compact\",\"context\",\"cost\",\"heapdump\",\"init\",\"review\",\"security-review\",\"extra-usage\",\"insights\",\"team-onboarding\"],\"apiKeySource\":\"none\",\"claude_code_version\":\"2.1.114\",\"output_style\":\"default\",\"agents\":[\"Explore\",\"general-purpose\",\"Plan\",\"statusline-setup\"],\"skills\":[\"update-config\",\"debug\",\"simplify\",\"batch\",\"fewer-permission-prompts\",\"loop\",\"schedule\",\"claude-api\"],\"plugins\":[],\"uuid\":\"46c2dd99-2f9b-4dab-9290-278ec4ca925f\",\"memory_paths\":{\"auto\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\1\\\\.claude\\\\projects\\\\C--Users-1-Documents-Local-First-Workflow-Dashboard\\\\memory\\\\\"},\"fast_mode_state\":\"off\"}\n.\\outputs\\sonnet-06C-1.out.jsonl:13:{\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_019aCaVkQKxV6FjPQPavNaZn\",\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"1\\t```context-pack\\n2\\t{\\n3\\t  \\\"diId\\\": \\\"06C-1\\\",\\n4\\t  \\\"requiredInputs\\\": [\\n5\\t    { \\\"path\\\": \\\"docs/directives/_header.md\\\", \\\"sha256\\\": \\\"b37a27f81792e82575a793f671839fdf463895e8ce4d1d4ccf7c5bea1213b2ee\\\" },\\n6\\t    { \\\"path\\\": \\\"docs/verification/_template.md\\\", \\\"sha256\\\": \\\"15f1b6dbdb703c94d6d7259b9417e17f438c980fad25b50b7ed96bc4da354b69\\\" },\\n7\\t    { \\\"path\\\": \\\"docs/plan/wp/WP-STATE-INTEGRITY-land-gate.md\\\", \\\"sha256\\\": \\\"2549764220878fe6e65e487973eeb0c1769dbeeee0083c5f98bc437b41c3354c\\\" }\\n8\\t  ],\\n9\\t  \\\"readOrder\\\": [\\n10\\t    \\\"docs/context/RUNTIME-INDEX.md\\\",\\n11\\t    \\\"docs/plan/wp/WP-STATE-INTEGRITY-land-gate.md\\\",\\n12\\t    \\\"docs/directives/_header.md\\\",\\n13\\t    \\\"docs/handoff/queue/directive-06C-1-statetransition-v2.md\\\"\\n14\\t  ],\\n15\\t  \\\"forbiddenActions\\\": [\\\"git push\\\", \\\"approve\\\", \\\"reject\\\", \\\"import\\\", \\\"spawn-executor\\\", \\\"edit-baseline\\\"]\\n16\\t}\\n17\\t```\\n18\\t\\n19\\t> **검수자 주(2026-07-13)**: 아래는 **사람이 준 설계 원문이다. 내용을 바꾸지 않았다.**\\n20\\t> 이 저장소의 기계 검사(context-pack-integrity·scope-check·발사기 claim)가 읽을 수 있도록 **위 Context Pack 블록과 아래 allowlist 절만** 검수자가 덧붙였다.\\n21\\t> **선행: 05H가 `HandoffIntegrityChecker.Run(ReconciliationOptions)`를 제공해야 한다.** `server/Harness/HandoffIntegrityCli.cs` 무접촉(05H).\\n22\\t> **단일 land gate**: \\u00005H·\\u00006C-1·\\u00006C-2·\\u00006H는 **통합 branch에서 함께** 넘긴다. **조각 land 금지.**\\n23\\t\\n24\\t---\\n25\\t# 06C-1 — StateTransition v2 core: reconciliation-먼저 + 결정적 candidate + rollback + high-risk fail-closed (sonnet)\\n26\\t\\n27\\t- actor: **CORE_INFRA_EXECUTOR (sonnet)** · WP-STATE-INTEGRITY · 단일 land gate\\n28\\t- 대상: `server/StateApplierCli.cs`, `state-transition` 모든 활성 호출자 정렬\\n29\\t- 선행: 05H가 `HandoffIntegrityChecker.Run(ReconciliationOptions)` + `lookupSuccess`(transitionContract 포함) 제공.\\n30\\t- 짝: 06C-2(trust-origin bootstrap)와 **같은 actor·같은 integration branch·하나의 land gate**. 지시서 분할 ≠ land 분할.\\n31\\t\\n32\\t---\\n33\\t\\n34\\t## 0. 실측된 결함 4개\\n35\\t\\n36\\t```csharp\\n37\\t// Step 1 sha256 → Step 2 IsAlreadyApplied면 즉시 ReportIdempotent(exit 0) → 그 다음 ApplyAndVerify\\n38\\t```\\n39\\t\\n40\\t- 결함 1(순서): idempotency가 pre-apply reconciliation보다 먼저 → 손 위조 가짜 id가 idempotent 성공.\\n41\\t- 결함 2(롤백 없음): Step 9/10 실패 시 `File.Move`된 WORKSTATE 원복 없음.\\n42\\t- 결함 3(비결정성): `BuildCandidate`가 `updatedAt`/`appliedAt`에 `UtcNow` 직접 호출.\\n43\\t- 결함 4(ID 결속 없음): id만 같으면 다른 request라도 idempotent 성공.\\n44\\t\\n45\\t## 1. 실행 순서 — pre-state hash는 \\\"미적용 ID일 때만\\\" (★ 정정)\\n46\\t\\n47\\t> pre-state hash를 idempotency보다 먼저 검사하면 정상 재시도가 죽는다: 최초 전이 성공 후 현재 state는\\n48\\t> 이미 P1(=expectedPost)이라, 같은 envelope 재적용 시 `expectedPre=P0 ≠ 현재=P1`로 sha256 거부되어\\n49\\t> idempotent 판정에 도달하지 못한다. 따라서 순서는:\\n50\\t\\n51\\t```text\\n52\\t1. envelope/request 파싱\\n53\\t2. 현재 state·log 로드\\n54\\t3. reconciliation (내부 checker, pending 없음)\\n55\\t     FAIL → 일반 전이 거부 exit 1 state-corrupted-preapply  (가짜 id 공격은 여기서 막힘)\\n56\\t4. existing-transition 판정 (§2)\\n57\\t     - transitionId가 이미 state+성공로그에 있음 → §2로 idempotent/collision 결정 (여기서 종료)\\n58\\t     - state에만 있고 성공로그 없음 → 이미 3의 reconciliation이 FAIL\\n59\\t     - 미적용 ID → 5로\\n60\\t5. (미적용 ID에 한해) 현재 state hash == envelope.expectedPreStateSha256   아니면 거부(안 씀)\\n61\\t6. request/candidate 검증 · 적용 (§4)\\n62\\t```\\n63\\t\\n64\\treconciliation이 가짜 id를 막고, pre-state 검사는 미적용 ID에만 적용되어 재시도가 산다.\\n65\\t\\n66\\t## 2. idempotency를 계약 hash에 결속 (결함 4 · v1 fail-closed)\\n67\\t\\n68\\t05H가 각 transitionId에 대해 `lookupSuccess(id)`를 반환한다:\\n69\\t`{ exists, schemaVersion, transitionContractSha256? }`.\\n70\\t\\n71\\tenvelope로부터 같은 방식으로 계약 hash를 계산한다:\\n72\\t\\n73\\t```text\\n74\\ttransitionContractSha256 = sha256(canonical{\\n75\\t  transitionId, transitionKind, requestSha256, preStateSha256(=expectedPre),\\n76\\t  postStateSha256(=expectedPost), effectiveAt })\\n77\\t```\\n78\\t\\n79\\t판정:\\n80\\t\\n81\\t```text\\n82\\t기존 ID + v2 로그 + contract hash 일치   → idempotent exit 0\\n83\\t기존 ID + v2 로그 + contract hash 불일치 → exit 1  transition-id-collision\\n84\\t기존 ID + v1 로그(내용 결속 불가)        → exit 1  legacy-idempotency-unverifiable\\n85\\t```\\n86\\t\\n87\\t과거 ID의 재적용을 자동 성공으로 인정하지 않는다.\\n88\\t\\n89\\t## 3. 결정적 BuildCandidate (결함 3)\\n90\\t\\n91\\t```text\\n92\\tCandidate = BuildCandidate(preState, request, transitionId, effectiveAt)   // 순수 함수\\n93\\t  updatedAt ← effectiveAt(날짜) · appliedTransitions[].appliedAt ← effectiveAt · UtcNow 호출 없음\\n94\\t```\\n95\\t\\n96\\t직렬화 계약 고정: UTF-8 no BOM · 고정 `JsonSerializerOptions`(`ProjectionCli.WriteOptions` 규약) ·\\n97\\t고정 들여쓰기 · 고정 newline · effectiveAt은 UTC RFC3339 · hash는 **실제로 쓰는 정확한 bytes**에 계산.\\n98\\t동일 입력 → 동일 bytes → 동일 SHA-256.\\n99\\t\\n100\\teffectiveAt 발급(외부 조작 금지): **NORMAL은 prepare가 현재 UTC를 직접 발급, 외부 `--effective-at` 금지.**\\n101\\tREPLAY/RECOVERY는 이번 WP fail-closed(§6).\\n102\\t\\n103\\t## 4. envelope + prepare/apply + 재계산-write (결함 2 · TOCTOU)\\n104\\t\\n105\\tenvelope:\\n106\\t\\n107\\t```json\\n108\\t{ \\\"schemaVersion\\\":1, \\\"transitionKind\\\":\\\"NORMAL\\\",\\n109\\t  \\\"transitionId\\\":\\\"…\\\", \\\"expectedPreStateSha256\\\":\\\"…\\\",\\n110\\t  \\\"requestPath\\\":\\\"…\\\", \\\"requestSha256\\\":\\\"…\\\", \\\"effectiveAt\\\":\\\"…\\\",\\n111\\t  \\\"expectedPostStateSha256\\\":\\\"…\\\", \\\"candidatePath\\\":\\\"outputs/state-transition/…candidate.json\\\" }\\n112\\t```\\n113\\t\\n114\\t- **prepare**(canonical 미수정): hash 계산 → effectiveAt 발급(NORMAL) → candidate 계산 →\\n115\\t  expectedPostStateSha256 = sha256(직렬화) → envelope+candidate를 `outputs/state-transition/`에 기록.\\n116\\t- **apply**(canonical 수정):\\n117\\t\\n118\\t```text\\n119\\t1. prepared candidate 파일 hash 확인 (evidence 무결성)\\n120\\t2. 현재 preState + request + envelope로 candidate를 메모리에서 재계산\\n121\\t3. 재계산 bytes hash == envelope.expectedPostStateSha256   아니면 거부(안 씀)\\n122\\t4. §1 순서: reconciliation → existing-transition → (미적용 시) pre-state hash → 검증\\n123\\t5. preimage = ReadAllBytes(WORKSTATE)\\n124\\t6. 재계산 bytes를 tmp에 쓰고 ProjectionCli.WriteAtomically 패턴으로 atomic replace\\n125\\t   ★ prepared candidate 파일은 evidence일 뿐 canonical write source 아님 (TOCTOU 차단)\\n126\\t7. 적용후: ProjectionCli.Run([\\\"projection\\\"]) · 내부 checker(PendingTransitionId=id) · v2 log append\\n127\\t```\\n128\\t\\n129\\t## 5. rollback + FATAL taxonomy (결함 2)\\n130\\t\\n131\\t```text\\n132\\t성공                                                          → exit 0\\n133\\t적용후 검사 실패 + 복원 성공 + 복원 hash==preimage + projection 성공  → exit 1 / ROLLED_BACK\\n134\\tpreimage 복원 실패  또는  복원 hash != preimage                 → exit 2 / FATAL_STATE_UNKNOWN (모든 자동작업 중단)\\n135\\t복원 성공 + projection 재생성 실패                              → exit 2 / STATE_RESTORED_PROJECTION_NOT_VERIFIED (HUMAN-INBOX)\\n136\\tlog append 성공 여부 불명                                       → exit 2 / AUDIT_LOG_STATE_UNKNOWN (다음 전이 금지)\\n137\\t```\\n138\\t\\n139\\t복원 직후 `sha256(WORKSTATE)==sha256(preimage)` 재검증 필수. v2 ok 로그는 성공 경로에서만 append.\\n140\\t**실패 주입은 결정적 test seam으로**(production 노출 플래그 금지) — 테스트 전용 DI/fake로 \\\"atomic replace 직후 실패\\\".\\n141\\t\\n142\\t## 6. transitionKind + high-risk fail-closed\\n143\\t\\n144\\tenvelope의 `transitionKind` ∈ {NORMAL, PHASE_CHANGE, RECOVERY, REPLAY}.\\n145\\t\\n146\\t```text\\n147\\tNORMAL → §1~5 그대로.\\n148\\tPHASE_CHANGE / RECOVERY / REPLAY → apply는 --human-receipt-id 요구, 신뢰 receipt ledger 조회·검증.\\n149\\t    이번 WP는 ledger 부재 → 항상 exit 1  trusted-human-receipt-required\\n150\\t```\\n151\\t\\n152\\t임의 경로 `--human-decision some-file.json`은 폐기. receipt 검증 계약의 골격만 남기고 활성화는\\n153\\t`WP-HUMAN-DECISION-PROVENANCE`로. 보고서에서 `CLAIMED_ACTOR`와 `VERIFIED_HUMAN_APPROVAL`을 섞지 않는다.\\n154\\t\\n155\\t## 7. 활성 호출자 정렬 + callsite gate\\n156\\t\\n157\\t`state-transition` 단일-샷을 쓰던 **활성** 경로를 prepare/apply로 정렬. 단, 옛 옵션은 기존 RECOVERY.md·\\n158\\t최초 StateApplier 지시서·실행 로그 등 **역사적 증거**에도 남아 있어 grep 결과를 전부 수정 대상으로 보면 안 된다.\\n159\\t신규 검사 `state-transition-callsite-check`:\\n160\\t\\n161\\t```text\\n162\\t범위: server/**/*.cs · scripts/** · outputs/launch/** · .claude/** · *.ps1 *.sh *.cmd *.bat ·\\n163\\t      운영 docs/prompts·templates · CI·manifest·JSON/YAML\\n164\\t판정: 활성 경로의 옛 단일-shot 호출 → 0 ; history/log/incident fixture의 옛 호출 → 명시 allowlist\\n165\\tevidence: { \\\"legacyCallsiteCount\\\":0, \\\"historicalReferenceCount\\\":N, \\\"classifiedPaths\\\":[…] }\\n166\\t```\\n167\\t\\n168\\tdi-completion-check는 `state-transition`을 직접 호출하지 않으므로 영향 없음. RECOVERY.md 수동 절차는 06H가 갱신.\\n169\\t\\n170\\t## 8. 완료 기준 (exit code)\\n171\\t\\n172\\t```text\\n173\\t1. dotnet build server -c Release                                  → 0\\n174\\t2. NORMAL prepare→apply 왕복                                        → 0   ★결함1\\n175\\t3. 같은 envelope 재적용 (최초 성공 후)                              → 0 idempotent  ★재시도 생존(순서 정정)\\n176\\t4. 손 위조: state에 가짜 id만, log엔 없음 → 전이                     → 1 state-corrupted-preapply  ★\\n177\\t5. 같은 id·다른 request(v2)                                        → 1 transition-id-collision  ★결함4\\n178\\t6. 기존 id가 v1 로그                                               → 1 legacy-idempotency-unverifiable\\n179\\t7. prepare 후 candidate 1바이트 변조 → apply                        → 거부(재계산 bytes로만 write) ★TOCTOU\\n180\\t8. test seam 적용후 실패 → 복원                                     → 1 ROLLED_BACK, WORKSTATE hash==preimage ★결함2\\n181\\t9. FATAL 4분기 각각 도달\\n182\\t10. transitionKind ∈ {PHASE_CHANGE,RECOVERY,REPLAY}                → 1 trusted-human-receipt-required\\n183\\t11. state-transition-callsite-check                               → legacyCallsiteCount 0\\n184\\t12. measure dev-pack                                              → 0\\n185\\t```\\n186\\t\\n187\\t## 9. 보고 / 스킬\\n188\\t\\n189\\tactor(sonnet)·명령과 exit·참조 스킬·`## 지표는 만족했으나 목적은 미달인 부분`(ADR-005).\\n190\\t\\n191\\t---\\n192\\t\\n193\\t## 허용 파일 (allowlist)\\n194\\t\\n195\\t- server/StateApplierCli.cs\\n196\\t- server/Harness/StateTransitionCallsiteCheckCli.cs\\n197\\t- server/Harness/HarnessRegistry.cs\\n198\\t- outputs/state-transition/**\\n199\\t- docs/verification/06c1-statetransition-v2.md\\n200\\t- docs/handoff/queue/directive-06C-1-statetransition-v2.md\\n201\\t\\n202\\t## 보고\\n203\\t\\n204\\tdocs/verification/_template.md 형식 그대로. **DI 유형 선언** · 유형별 필수 검증 · 하네스별 **기대 exit vs 실제 exit** · 실패 분류(v9 §0.3) · 잔여 위험 · **`## 지표는 만족했으나 목적은 미달인 부분`**(ADR-005).\\n205\\t**자기보고는 증거가 아니다** — 검수자가 land gate를 직접 재실행한다. 못 한 시험은 `NOT_VERIFIED`. **숨기면 반려다.**\"}]},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"3f491dce-b311-474d-b5b2-b12e21a0d522\",\"uuid\":\"31487f80-bf03-474c-b1db-d2706ec4b2a6\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-13T13:36:50.537Z\",\"tool_use_result\":{\"type\":\"text\",\"file\":{\"filePath\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\1\\\\Documents\\\\Local-First Workflow Dashboard\\\\docs\\\\handoff\\\\queue\\\\directive-06C-1-statetransition-v2.md\",\"content\":\"```context-pack\\n{\\n  \\\"diId\\\": \\\"06C-1\\\",\\n  \\\"requiredInputs\\\": [\\n    { \\\"path\\\": \\\"docs/directives/_header.md\\\", \\\"sha256\\\": \\\"b37a27f81792e82575a793f671839fdf463895e8ce4d1d4ccf7c5bea1213b2ee\\\" },\\n    { \\\"path\\\": \\\"docs/verification/_template.md\\\", \\\"sha256\\\": \\\"15f1b6dbdb703c94d6d7259b9417e17f438c980fad25b50b7ed96bc4da354b69\\\" },\\n    { \\\"path\\\": \\\"docs/plan/wp/WP-STATE-INTEGRITY-land-gate.md\\\", \\\"sha256\\\": \\\"2549764220878fe6e65e487973eeb0c1769dbeeee0083c5f98bc437b41c3354c\\\" }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"readOrder\\\": [\\n    \\\"docs/context/RUNTIME-INDEX.md\\\",\\n    \\\"docs/plan/wp/WP-STATE-INTEGRITY-land-gate.md\\\",\\n    \\\"docs/directives/_header.md\\\",\\n    \\\"docs/handoff/queue/directive-06C-1-statetransition-v2.md\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"forbiddenActions\\\": [\\\"git push\\\", \\\"approve\\\", \\\"reject\\\", \\\"import\\\", \\\"spawn-executor\\\", \\\"edit-baseline\\\"]\\n}\\n```\\n\\n> **검수자 주(2026-07-13)**: 아래는 **사람이 준 설계 원문이다. 내용을 바꾸지 않았다.**\\n> 이 저장소의 기계 검사(context-pack-integrity·scope-check·발사기 claim)가 읽을 수 있도록 **위 Context Pack 블록과 아래 allowlist 절만** 검수자가 덧붙였다.\\n> **선행: 05H가 `HandoffIntegrityChecker.Run(ReconciliationOptions)`를 제공해야 한다.** `server/Harness/HandoffIntegrityCli.cs` 무접촉(05H).\\n> **단일 land gate**: \\u00005H·\\u00006C-1·\\u00006C-2·\\u00006H는 **통합 branch에서 함께** 넘긴다. **조각 land 금지.**\\n\\n---\\n# 06C-1 — StateTransition v2 core: reconciliation-먼저 + 결정적 candidate + rollback + high-risk fail-closed (sonnet)\\n\\n- actor: **CORE_INFRA_EXECUTOR (sonnet)** · WP-STATE-INTEGRITY · 단일 land gate\\n- 대상: `server/StateApplierCli.cs`, `state-transition` 모든 활성 호출자 정렬\\n- 선행: 05H가 `HandoffIntegrityChecker.Run(ReconciliationOptions)` + `lookupSuccess`(transitionContract 포함) 제공.\\n- 짝: 06C-2(trust-origin bootstrap)와 **같은 actor·같은 integration branch·하나의 land gate**. 지시서 분할 ≠ land 분할.\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 0. 실측된 결함 4개\\n\\n```csharp\\n// Step 1 sha256 → Step 2 IsAlreadyApplied면 즉시 ReportIdempotent(exit 0) → 그 다음 ApplyAndVerify\\n```\\n\\n- 결함 1(순서): idempotency가 pre-apply reconciliation보다 먼저 → 손 위조 가짜 id가 idempotent 성공.\\n- 결함 2(롤백 없음): Step 9/10 실패 시 `File.Move`된 WORKSTATE 원복 없음.\\n- 결함 3(비결정성): `BuildCandidate`가 `updatedAt`/`appliedAt`에 `UtcNow` 직접 호출.\\n- 결함 4(ID 결속 없음): id만 같으면 다른 request라도 idempotent 성공.\\n\\n## 1. 실행 순서 — pre-state hash는 \\\"미적용 ID일 때만\\\" (★ 정정)\\n\\n> pre-state hash를 idempotency보다 먼저 검사하면 정상 재시도가 죽는다: 최초 전이 성공 후 현재 state는\\n> 이미 P1(=expectedPost)이라, 같은 envelope 재적용 시 `expectedPre=P0 ≠ 현재=P1`로 sha256 거부되어\\n> idempotent 판정에 도달하지 못한다. 따라서 순서는:\\n\\n```text\\n1. envelope/request 파싱\\n2. 현재 state·log 로드\\n3. reconciliation (내부 checker, pending 없음)\\n     FAIL → 일반 전이 거부 exit 1 state-corrupted-preapply  (가짜 id 공격은 여기서 막힘)\\n4. existing-transition 판정 (§2)\\n     - transitionId가 이미 state+성공로그에 있음 → §2로 idempotent/collision 결정 (여기서 종료)\\n     - state에만 있고 성공로그 없음 → 이미 3의 reconciliation이 FAIL\\n     - 미적용 ID → 5로\\n5. (미적용 ID에 한해) 현재 state hash == envelope.expectedPreStateSha256   아니면 거부(안 씀)\\n6. request/candidate 검증 · 적용 (§4)\\n```\\n\\nreconciliation이 가짜 id를 막고, pre-state 검사는 미적용 ID에만 적용되어 재시도가 산다.\\n\\n## 2. idempotency를 계약 hash에 결속 (결함 4 · v1 fail-closed)\\n\\n05H가 각 transitionId에 대해 `lookupSuccess(id)`를 반환한다:\\n`{ exists, schemaVersion, transitionContractSha256? }`.\\n\\nenvelope로부터 같은 방식으로 계약 hash를 계산한다:\\n\\n```text\\ntransitionContractSha256 = sha256(canonical{\\n  transitionId, transitionKind, requestSha256, preStateSha256(=expectedPre),\\n  postStateSha256(=expectedPost), effectiveAt })\\n```\\n\\n판정:\\n\\n```text\\n기존 ID + v2 로그 + contract hash 일치   → idempotent exit 0\\n기존 ID + v2 로그 + contract hash 불일치 → exit 1  transition-id-collision\\n기존 ID + v1 로그(내용 결속 불가)        → exit 1  legacy-idempotency-unverifiable\\n```\\n\\n과거 ID의 재적용을 자동 성공으로 인정하지 않는다.\\n\\n## 3. 결정적 BuildCandidate (결함 3)\\n\\n```text\\nCandidate = BuildCandidate(preState, request, transitionId, effectiveAt)   // 순수 함수\\n  updatedAt ← effectiveAt(날짜) · appliedTransitions[].appliedAt ← effectiveAt · UtcNow 호출 없음\\n```\\n\\n직렬화 계약 고정: UTF-8 no BOM · 고정 `JsonSerializerOptions`(`ProjectionCli.WriteOptions` 규약) ·\\n고정 들여쓰기 · 고정 newline · effectiveAt은 UTC RFC3339 · hash는 **실제로 쓰는 정확한 bytes**에 계산.\\n동일 입력 → 동일 bytes → 동일 SHA-256.\\n\\neffectiveAt 발급(외부 조작 금지): **NORMAL은 prepare가 현재 UTC를 직접 발급, 외부 `--effective-at` 금지.**\\nREPLAY/RECOVERY는 이번 WP fail-closed(§6).\\n\\n## 4. envelope + prepare/apply + 재계산-write (결함 2 · TOCTOU)\\n\\nenvelope:\\n\\n```json\\n{ \\\"schemaVersion\\\":1, \\\"transitionKind\\\":\\\"NORMAL\\\",\\n  \\\"transitionId\\\":\\\"…\\\", \\\"expectedPreStateSha256\\\":\\\"…\\\",\\n  \\\"requestPath\\\":\\\"…\\\", \\\"requestSha256\\\":\\\"…\\\", \\\"effectiveAt\\\":\\\"…\\\",\\n  \\\"expectedPostStateSha256\\\":\\\"…\\\", \\\"candidatePath\\\":\\\"outputs/state-transition/…candidate.json\\\" }\\n```\\n\\n- **prepare**(canonical 미수정): hash 계산 → effectiveAt 발급(NORMAL) → candidate 계산 →\\n  expectedPostStateSha256 = sha256(직렬화) → envelope+candidate를 `outputs/state-transition/`에 기록.\\n- **apply**(canonical 수정):\\n\\n```text\\n1. prepared candidate 파일 hash 확인 (evidence 무결성)\\n2. 현재 preState + request + envelope로 candidate를 메모리에서 재계산\\n3. 재계산 bytes hash == envelope.expectedPostStateSha256   아니면 거부(안 씀)\\n4. §1 순서: reconciliation → existing-transition → (미적용 시) pre-state hash → 검증\\n5. preimage = ReadAllBytes(WORKSTATE)\\n6. 재계산 bytes를 tmp에 쓰고 ProjectionCli.WriteAtomically 패턴으로 atomic replace\\n   ★ prepared candidate 파일은 evidence일 뿐 canonical write source 아님 (TOCTOU 차단)\\n7. 적용후: ProjectionCli.Run([\\\"projection\\\"]) · 내부 checker(PendingTransitionId=id) · v2 log append\\n```\\n\\n## 5. rollback + FATAL taxonomy (결함 2)\\n\\n```text\\n성공                                                          → exit 0\\n적용후 검사 실패 + 복원 성공 + 복원 hash==preimage + projection 성공  → exit 1 / ROLLED_BACK\\npreimage 복원 실패  또는  복원 hash != preimage                 → exit 2 / FATAL_STATE_UNKNOWN (모든 자동작업 중단)\\n복원 성공 + projection 재생성 실패                              → exit 2 / STATE_RESTORED_PROJECTION_NOT_VERIFIED (HUMAN-INBOX)\\nlog append 성공 여부 불명                                       → exit 2 / AUDIT_LOG_STATE_UNKNOWN (다음 전이 금지)\\n```\\n\\n복원 직후 `sha256(WORKSTATE)==sha256(preimage)` 재검증 필수. v2 ok 로그는 성공 경로에서만 append.\\n**실패 주입은 결정적 test seam으로**(production 노출 플래그 금지) — 테스트 전용 DI/fake로 \\\"atomic replace 직후 실패\\\".\\n\\n## 6. transitionKind + high-risk fail-closed\\n\\nenvelope의 `transitionKind` ∈ {NORMAL, PHASE_CHANGE, RECOVERY, REPLAY}.\\n\\n```text\\nNORMAL → §1~5 그대로.\\nPHASE_CHANGE / RECOVERY / REPLAY → apply는 --human-receipt-id 요구, 신뢰 receipt ledger 조회·검증.\\n    이번 WP는 ledger 부재 → 항상 exit 1  trusted-human-receipt-required\\n```\\n\\n임의 경로 `--human-decision some-file.json`은 폐기. receipt 검증 계약의 골격만 남기고 활성화는\\n`WP-HUMAN-DECISION-PROVENANCE`로. 보고서에서 `CLAIMED_ACTOR`와 `VERIFIED_HUMAN_APPROVAL`을 섞지 않는다.\\n\\n## 7. 활성 호출자 정렬 + callsite gate\\n\\n`state-transition` 단일-샷을 쓰던 **활성** 경로를 prepare/apply로 정렬. 단, 옛 옵션은 기존 RECOVERY.md·\\n최초 StateApplier 지시서·실행 로그 등 **역사적 증거**에도 남아 있어 grep 결과를 전부 수정 대상으로 보면 안 된다.\\n신규 검사 `state-transition-callsite-check`:\\n\\n```text\\n범위: server/**/*.cs · scripts/** · outputs/launch/** · .claude/** · *.ps1 *.sh *.cmd *.bat ·\\n      운영 docs/prompts·templates · CI·manifest·JSON/YAML\\n판정: 활성 경로의 옛 단일-shot 호출 → 0 ; history/log/incident fixture의 옛 호출 → 명시 allowlist\\nevidence: { \\\"legacyCallsiteCount\\\":0, \\\"historicalReferenceCount\\\":N, \\\"classifiedPaths\\\":[…] }\\n```\\n\\ndi-completion-check는 `state-transition`을 직접 호출하지 않으므로 영향 없음. RECOVERY.md 수동 절차는 06H가 갱신.\\n\\n## 8. 완료 기준 (exit code)\\n\\n```text\\n1. dotnet build server -c Release                                  → 0\\n2. NORMAL prepare→apply 왕복                                        → 0   ★결함1\\n3. 같은 envelope 재적용 (최초 성공 후)                              → 0 idempotent  ★재시도 생존(순서 정정)\\n4. 손 위조: state에 가짜 id만, log엔 없음 → 전이                     → 1 state-corrupted-preapply  ★\\n5. 같은 id·다른 request(v2)                                        → 1 transition-id-collision  ★결함4\\n6. 기존 id가 v1 로그                                               → 1 legacy-idempotency-unverifiable\\n7. prepare 후 candidate 1바이트 변조 → apply                        → 거부(재계산 bytes로만 write) ★TOCTOU\\n8. test seam 적용후 실패 → 복원                                     → 1 ROLLED_BACK, WORKSTATE hash==preimage ★결함2\\n9. FATAL 4분기 각각 도달\\n10. transitionKind ∈ {PHASE_CHANGE,RECOVERY,REPLAY}                → 1 trusted-human-receipt-required\\n11. state-transition-callsite-check                               → legacyCallsiteCount 0\\n12. measure dev-pack                                              → 0\\n```\\n\\n## 9. 보고 / 스킬\\n\\nactor(sonnet)·명령과 exit·참조 스킬·`## 지표는 만족했으나 목적은 미달인 부분`(ADR-005).\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 허용 파일 (allowlist)\\n\\n- server/StateApplierCli.cs\\n- server/Harness/StateTransitionCallsiteCheckCli.cs\\n- server/Harness/HarnessRegistry.cs\\n- outputs/state-transition/**\\n- docs/verification/06c1-statetransition-v2.md\\n- docs/handoff/queue/directive-06C-1-statetransition-v2.md\\n\\n## 보고\\n\\ndocs/verification/_template.md 형식 그대로. **DI 유형 선언** · 유형별 필수 검증 · 하네스별 **기대 exit vs 실제 exit** · 실패 분류(v9 §0.3) · 잔여 위험 · **`## 지표는 만족했으나 목적은 미달인 부분`**(ADR-005).\\n**자기보고는 증거가 아니다** — 검수자가 land gate를 직접 재실행한다. 못 한 시험은 `NOT_VERIFIED`. **숨기면 반려다.**\",\"numLines\":205,\"startLine\":1,\"totalLines\":205}}}\n.\\outputs\\sonnet-06C-1.out.jsonl:36:{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_011Ccz9VJLvQoeKDDKB8HUVe\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"OK, now I have a clear picture. Let me understand what needs to be done:\\n\\n## Summary of what needs to be done for 06C-1\\n\\n### Current code problems in `StateApplierCli.cs`:\\n\\n1. **결함 1 (순서)**: In `Run()`, Step 2 (idempotency check) happens before reconciliation. The correct order is:\\n   1. envelope/request 파싱\\n   2. 현재 state·log 로드\\n   3. **reconciliation** (먼저)\\n   4. **existing-transition** 판정\\n   5. (미적용 ID에 한해) pre-state hash 검사\\n   6. request/candidate 검증·적용\\n\\n2. **결함 2 (롤백 없음)**: If post-apply fails, there's no rollback. Need to save `preimage` and restore if failure occurs.\\n\\n3. **결함 3 (비결정성)**: `BuildCandidate` uses `DateTime.UtcNow` directly. Need to accept `effectiveAt` parameter.\\n\\n4. **결함 4 (ID 결속 없음)**: Idempotency check only checks if ID exists in appliedTransitions, doesn't verify the content matches what was actually applied.\\n\\nNow I need to redesign the CLI around a v2 envelope structure with separate `prepare` and `apply` commands. The prepare phase computes the hash, effectiveAt timestamp, candidate, and expected post-state hash, writing these to outputs. The apply phase reads the envelope, verifies it, and applies the transition atomically with rollback capability. I'm also introducing transition kinds—NORMAL, PHASE_CHANGE, RECOVERY, REPLAY—where high-risk ones fail closed. The v2 log format needs to capture schemaVersion, transitionKind, request and state hashes, transition contract hash, and effectiveAt. Before any state change happens, I should run the HandoffIntegrityChecker to reconcile first.\\n\\nFor safety, I'm adding rollback by saving the preimage before writing and restoring on failure, plus TOCTOU protection by recomputing the candidate from memory rather than using the prepared file for the actual write. I need a test seam to inject failures after write for testing rollback scenarios, and a new harness to check for legacy single-shot calls. The new CLI replaces the current single `state-transition` command with `prepare` and `apply` subcommands—prepare takes the request path and optional transition ID, outputting the envelope and candidate to the state-transition directory, while apply reads the envelope path to verify and execute the transition. After writing the bytes atomically to the work state file, I run the projection CLI to apply the transition, which internally validates the pending transition ID and appends to the v2 log. The envelope structure captures all the necessary metadata—schema version, transition kind, IDs, hashes for both pre and post states, the request details, and the path to the candidate file—so the apply phase can fully reconstruct and verify the state change before committing it.\\n\\nI notice the codebase already has a `--root` flag for specifying a custom root directory, and the directive explicitly says not to create new production path flags like that since they become canonical bypass routes. The `--dry-run` option already exists in the StateApplierCli, so for testing I should use temporary copies of the repository instead of adding new flags.\\n\\nFor the test fixtures to work properly with prepare/apply operations, I need a WORKSTATE with valid canonical IDs that match the required patterns—phaseId, wpId, and diId all need to conform to their respective formats. Looking at fixture-c, I'm noticing the IDs don't actually match the expected patterns: \\\"WP-TEST\\\" fails the `^WP-\\\\d{2,}$` check, \\\"DI-TEST-C\\\" doesn't match `^DI-\\\\d{2}-\\\\d{2,}$`, though \\\"P00\\\" does pass validation. I need to figure out which tests actually require state copies versus running on the canonical state. Looking at the test descriptions, tests 2, 3, 5, 6, 7, and 8 all mention \\\"사본\\\" (copy), meaning they need temporary modified versions of the repo, while test 4 runs on the canonical state to verify it properly rejects corruption. The new `state-transition` command will need to support various flags and options to handle these different test scenarios. So the directive is saying I need to update the active code paths that currently call the old single-shot `state-transition` command to use the new `prepare/apply` pattern instead. The old calling convention with its options will still exist in historical records like recovery documentation and logs, but those shouldn't all be treated as things to update—only the active callers need to be migrated. I'm trying to identify which parts of the codebase are actively using the old single-shot approach so I can convert them.\\n\\nThe key issue is that `RunPostApply` currently invokes the handoff integrity check through the old CLI interface, but it should be refactored to call the checker directly in-process using the new API. I'm starting to map out how to restructure the CLI to support both the new `prepare` and `apply` subcommands while potentially maintaining backward compatibility with the existing single-shot entry point.\\n\\nActually, rereading the requirements more carefully—the directive is clear that the new interface should be `prepare` and `apply` subcommands, not the old single-shot approach. So the `Run` method needs to become a dispatcher that routes based on the subcommand argument, with `prepare` and `apply` handling their respective workflows, and the old behavior should be phased out in favor of this new structure.\\n\\nFor the test seam around rollback failures, I need a way to inject failures deterministically without exposing test flags in production. An environment variable could work for CLI testing, but the directive explicitly forbids production-exposed flags. I'm thinking through how to set up a test hook that's only available during testing without polluting the production code path. The challenge is that tests run via CLI invocation, so I need a way to inject failures that doesn't expose test hooks to production. A dependency injection or fake approach would work for unit tests, but here we're calling the CLI directly. I could either add a hidden test-specific flag, create a separate test command variant, or use an internal static field that gets set during test execution.\\n\\nThe key constraint is that the flag can't be visible in normal CLI help or usage. A dedicated `test-seam` subcommand seems cleanest—it wouldn't appear in the production CLI router, so even though it exists in the binary, it's not exposed to users.\\n\\nAlternatively, I could use a static delegate or action that tests can inject into, triggered either by an undocumented environment variable or a hidden test command. The environment variable approach is simpler for CLI testing since I can just set it before running the apply command without needing a separate subcommand invocation.\\n\\nFor the full design, I'm thinking of adding a test-specific subcommand like `state-transition test-seam-apply-and-fail` that wraps the apply logic but injects the failure point, or just relying on the environment variable check within the normal apply path.\\n\\nNow I need to reconsider whether the prepare command should run reconciliation—it probably shouldn't, since prepare is just about computing the transition envelope, not validating the current state. So reconciliation runs during apply, not prepare—that makes sense since prepare doesn't touch the canonical state. Looking at the §1 sequence, it's envelope parsing, loading current state and log, then reconciliation as an internal check before deciding whether to accept the transition or fail with state-corrupted-preapply.\\n\\nFor prepare, I'm debating whether to add reconciliation as an early safety check even though the directive only explicitly requires it in apply. Since prepare only writes to outputs and doesn't modify canonical state, it's not strictly necessary, but it could catch issues earlier. I'll include it for robustness.\\n\\nNow I need to figure out the `transitionContractSha256` calculation—it should hash a canonical JSON object containing the transition ID, kind, request hash, pre and post state hashes, and effective timestamp, using sorted keys to ensure consistency.\\n\\nFor the applier log format, I'm structuring a v2 schema that captures the transition result along with all the relevant hashes and metadata needed for verification. I'm also considering how to implement atomic writes using the ProjectionCli pattern to ensure data integrity.\\n\\nNow I need to identify which files require changes: the StateApplierCli needs a major rewrite to support the prepare/apply workflow, I'll need to create a new harness for state transition callsite checking, register it in the harness registry, and set up the output directory structure for storing prepare/apply artifacts at runtime.\\n\\nLet me verify the allowlist constraints and then examine ProjectionCli.cs to understand the WriteAtomically pattern, plus check the existing HarnessRegistry to see how to properly register a new harness.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"stop_details\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":660,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":59466,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":660},\"output_tokens\":36,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"},\"context_management\":null},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"3f491dce-b311-474d-b5b2-b12e21a0d522\",\"uuid\":\"6507b65d-3dde-404d-9519-f258170dee3e\"}\n.\\outputs\\sonnet-06C-1.out.jsonl:52:{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_011Ccz9eYaSC4o1NEhwfr59r\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"Now I have a clear picture. Let me also check the WP-REGISTRY.json to understand what WP IDs are valid for testing, and check if there's a `WP-TEST` or similar entry.\\n\\nActually, looking at fixture-c, it has `wpId: \\\"WP-TEST\\\"` and `diId: \\\"DI-TEST-C\\\"`. But the validator checks these with regex:\\n- phaseId: `^P\\\\d{2,}$` - \\\"P00\\\" would pass but fixture-c doesn't have phaseId... wait it does: `\\\"phaseId\\\": \\\"P00\\\"` - this passes\\n- wpId: `^WP-\\\\d{2,}$` - \\\"WP-TEST\\\" doesn't match\\n- diId: `^DI-\\\\d{2}-\\\\d{2,}$` - \\\"DI-TEST-C\\\" doesn't match\\n\\nSo fixture-c only works for reconciliation testing since it has invalid canonical IDs. For prepare/apply testing, I need a proper WORKSTATE with valid IDs, a registered WP in the registry, and a valid application configur